snippet.title: Spider-Man 2: The Game E3 2003 trailer HQ
snippet.description: Reuploaded in high quality. The very rare E3 2003 trailer for Spider-Man 2: The Game featuring the Lizard, who was unfortunately cut from the game. Watch my original video for a better description.
